name: Waiting
description:
2nd travel photo of a cat named Charcoal and his goldfish friend. This picture is called waiting. They are waiting for the train to use as a means of transportation.
it's a bit annoyed because the train is coming too late and there's a sloth as the driver. Fortunately them not lonely because there are other friends waiting for this train as well.. I believe that every wait has meaning, some people wait for their loved ones, some people wait for a chance to succeed in life. I'm rooting for every wait.
